fields.title: focus-2-admin
fields.description:
Focus is a free Bootstrap 4 admin dashboard website template. This template will be the perfect solution if you are looking for a backend dashboard or an admin dashboard. It developed with a clean and simple design and also got many effective features. Moreover, this fantastic dashboard is 100% responsive and highly well crafted with all the latest retina screens and devices. While exploring you will understand it’s not just a dashboard, it’s a fully functional management platform.

Free Bootstrap 4 HTML5 Admin Dashboard Website Template

Focus offers two types of admin dashboards, and they are totally unique from one another. It also includes some awesome features like a collapsible navigation bar, sticky top navigation bar, various types of charts, bootstrap components, widgets, forms, authentication pages, error pages, and more. This dashboard template comes with all of the functionality you’ll need to get your web project off the ground. You can also customize it without any difficulties with its well-structured code. So hurry up and download Focus to strike online using the most cutting-edge technologies.

fields.title: majestic-Dashcoard
fields.description:
Majestic Admin is a free Bootstrap admin dashboard template. It is simple yet powerful and built with the latest Bootstrap 4 framework, SAAS, jQuery, HTML5, and CSS3. Moreover, It best suits website backend, web app, and admin panels. It is highly responsiveness and looks perfect on any device whether it is mobile or desktop.

Free HTML5 Bootstrap 4 Admin Dashboard Template

Besides, essential features like charts, tables, user pages, custom UI elements and forms are available with this template. Creation and customization are very simpler with Majestic Admin. A clean and well-managed code inside the box will make it easy to build even for beginners. Create and get a stunning project with Majestic Admin.
